Text: Hello,I thought this project I would list the questions from the blog guide and answer them underneath.

What would I do differently if I would be faced with the same situation or goals?
So far not much.
I think we are going to probably do some group coding which would be good and maybe help generate solutions better.
I decided before the break that i want to practice being less domineering in a team setting.
I am hoping Koko and /or someone else in the group acts as project leader as it will make this easier.
I have discussed this already with Koko but will make it clear next week that i want to play a supporting role in the project.
For this reason I think I was too definite in the way i discussed theÂ methodology in the presentation as I didn't really discuss it enough with the team first.

I think the poster and figuring out a viable path for the methodology was pretty good.
It needs to be much more defined by the end of this week though.
